  <prompt>
    Author the new `SessionFileEnrichmentService` under `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Sessions/` (or appropriate location — verify via grep for existing peer services like `SessionPersistenceService`). The service orchestrates upload-time enrichment per architecture/stateful-chat-architecture.md §4.4 + §6.1: parallel invocation of `FileClassificationService` (067) + `FileSummarizationService` (068) + `FileManifestExtractor` (069), then persistence of the enriched `ChatSessionFile` via `SessionPersistenceService.UpdateUploadedFilesAsync` (072). Concrete-class injection per ADR-010 — do NOT use `IServiceProvider.GetService&lt;T&gt;()`. Method signature: `Task&lt;EnrichedChatSessionFile&gt; EnrichAsync(string sessionId, string fileId, string fileName, string contentType, string textContent, CancellationToken ct)`.
  </prompt>

  <role>SPAARKE platform BFF developer. Expert in `Services/Ai/Sessions/` layer + async parallel orchestration + ADR-010 DI minimalism.</role>

  <goal>
    `SessionFileEnrichmentService.cs` exists with the orchestrator class + `ISessionFileEnrichmentService` interface. Service composes the 3 enrichment services in parallel (`Task.WhenAll`), assembles an `EnrichedChatSessionFile` record (or equivalent shape per task 071's `ChatSession.UploadedFiles` shape), and returns it. Constructor takes `IFileClassificationService`, `IFileSummarizationService`, `IFileManifestExtractor` via concrete-typed injection. Build passes. Unit-test stub authored.
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      Per architecture §4.4 (New components introduced) + §6.1 (Upload pipeline data flow). The 4 enrichment services (066, 067, 068, 069) are authored in parallel in wave 4-B; their DI registration is task 070. The output shape is consumed by 071 (`ChatSession.UploadedFiles` extension) and persisted by 072 (`SessionPersistenceService.UpdateUploadedFilesAsync`). Target performance: 4 parallel paths complete ≤4s for a 50-page PDF (task 073 enforces).
    </background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Sessions/SessionPersistenceService.cs</file>
